I don't see Struct or Map type ColumnStatsData in org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.api like there are ColumnStatsData types for primitives eg: BooleanColumnStatsData. As far as I can tell this is not supported by default - we may have to implement something on our own.
@rschlussel  let me know your thoughts regarding this and we can create a task/issue for it.

